- content_for(:body_id) {"home"}
- content_for(:lang) {"en"}

%section#start
  %hgroup
    %h1
      %img{:alt => "Rubyconf Argentina | Octubre 24 / 25, 2014", :height => "244", :src => "images/rubyconf.png", :width => "462"}
    %h2 Ciudad Cultural Konex

%section#registration
  %article.wrapper
    %h2 Registration
    .content
      %p
        %a.btn.btn-alt{href: '#'} 
          Soon
          %i.fa.fa-angle-right

      %p What you get with your ticket:

      %ul
        %li Admission to two days of talk sessions
        %li Access to any after-hour parties
        %li Official Conference T-Shirt and goodie bag
        %li Breakfast, lunch and snacks on both days
        %li Access to our fantastic attendees and speakers!

%section#speakers
  %article.wrapper
    %h2 Speakers
    .content

      %p
        So you think you have a crazy idea that no one would ever consider presenting in a conference? 
        %br
        That no conference committee would accept? Now we are talking. 
      %p 
        Read the 
        %a{href: "call_for_papers_en.html" } guidelines and submit your proposal 
        and get to talk in front of more than 400 rubyists! 
      %p 
        We want you to speak at the next RubyConf Argentina.
      %p
        %a.btn{:href=>"call_for_papers_en.html"}
          Call For Papers
          %i.fa.fa-angle-right

%section#sponsors
  %article.wrapper
    %h2 Sponsors
    .content
      %h3
        Are you interested in helping us organize the 4th RubyConf Argentina?
      %p 
        Your company can be part of one of the biggest conferences in South America. 

      / %p
      /   %a.btn.btn-alt{:href=>"/assets/SponsorsBrochure2014.pdf"} Download Brochure
      %p 
        %a.btn.btn-alt{:href=>"mailto:rubyconfar@gmail.com?&subject=[RubyConfAr] About sponsoring the event."} Contact us
        and we'll tell you how to take advantage of this opportunity.

